data.name: customSqlQuery1.Sql
data.value: select distinct *, (select x.PackingMth from mercedesdb..PackingMonths x where x.Id=a.PackingMonthId) as PackingMonth, (select x.ModelVarian from mercedesdb..VarianDetails x where x.Id=a.VarianId) as Varian, (select y.VarianName from mercedesdb..varians y where y.Id=(select x.VarianId from mercedesdb..VarianDetails x where x.Id=a.VarianId)) as Model from mercedesdb..jobcard a left join (select JobCardId,AssemblySectionName from mercedesdb..JobCardDetail)b on a.Id=b.JobCardId where a.id=41 and AssemblySectionName='Mechanical line Subassembly' order by b.AssemblySectionName
